title: (Mon Full) Lunchbox Thinks The Doll Is Messing with Him + Our Studio Breaks! + Bobby’s Dilemma with Upcoming Garth Brooks Performance
itunes:title: (Mon Full) Lunchbox Thinks The Doll Is Messing with Him + Our Studio Breaks! + Bobby’s Dilemma with Upcoming Garth Brooks Performance
description:
Lunchbox thinks the doll is messing with him after getting an insane amount of charges on his credit card. And then shortly after that…our entire studio breaks! Could it be the doll messing with us? Bobby shares the dilemma he and the Raging Idiots are having going into their show with Garth Brooks.
